The Planewalker's Guild is an old guild, dating back to before the time the Great Upheaval. The guild is newly returned to Sigil, having spent nearly a millenium based on the Infinite Staircase.
Its a guild that believes that only travelling the planes can reveal the true nature of the Multiverse.
Their guild-master is Balthasar Thames the Knowledgeable and their headquarters is in the Market Ward of Sigil. 

